INSTALL
=======

ONTO-Toolkit requires:

1. Galaxy (latest version recommended):

	http://main.g2.bx.psu.edu/

2. Thea

	http://github.com/vangelis/thea

3. SWI-Prolog (required by Thea)

   http://swi-prolog.org
	
After installing the required software:

1. copy tools to '$GALAXY_HOME/tools/'

  cp -pr tools/* $GALAXY_HOME/tools/

2. Copy the test data files to '$GALAXY_HOME/test-data/'

3. Adapt your 'tool_conf.xml' file by adding the 'Thea-Galaxy' section:

  TODO

4. Restart your Galaxy instance.
